name: The Reverb Conspiracy  - Volume One
description:
The Reverberation Appreciation Society (producers of Austin Psych Fest) and Fuzz Club Records teamed up to release a 2x LP European Psych compilation - The Reverb Conspiracy, was released on November 10th 2012, and celebrated by a two day event at Shakewell Arms in London followed by a 2 week european tour. 

The album’s tracklist spans the continent and documenting the darker side of Europe’s psychedelic rock scene with songs from 19 bands, curated by Fuzz Club Records. 

The compilation is be available in a limited, hand numbered edition of 1000 2x 180g LP with deluxe packaging and artwork from Nonni Dead (from The Dead Skeletons).
All songs has been mastered by Brett Orrison (The Black Angels live sound engineer) specially for this vinyl release.

The Reverb Conspiracy - Volume One 

1. Black Market Karma (UK) - Weightless 
2. A Victim Of Society (GR) - You're Gonna Hate Me
3. The Lucid Dream (UK) - Hits Me Like I'm Stoned 
4. The Koolaid Electric Company (UK)- Dreams

5. The Orange Revival (SE) - Ever
6. The KVB (UK) - Never Enough
7. Radar Men From The Moon (NL) - Heading For The Void
8. Singapore Sling (IS) - Nothing Inside
9. Oscar Suave (UK) - No Direction

10. Dead Skeletons (IS) - Kundalini Eyes
11. Lola Colt (UK) - Diamonds 
12. Sonic Jesus (IT) - Underground
13. The Underground Youth (UK) - I Need You
14. Black Lizard (FL) - Spirits

15. Wall Of Death (FR) - Thunder Sky
16. Get Your Gun (DK) - Staying For A While
17. The Third Sound (IS) - Re-Elevation
18. The Wands (DK) - Hello I Know The Blow You Grow Is Magic
19. Dead Rabbits (UK) - When I'm Blue

name: Dead Rabbits - The Ticket That Exploded
description: After what seemed like years of waiting Dead Rabbits have finally put the finishing touches to their triumphant debut album 'The Ticket That Exploded'.

name: Electric Eye - Pick Up, Lift Off, Space, Time
description:
One of the most exciting new band from Norway's musical capital, Bergen! Electric Eye is psychedelic space-rock made up by dirty blues, reverb and groovy drones. Walking in the shadows of modern psych-rockers The Black Angels, Wooden Shjips and The Warlocks, Electric Eye also invokes freak-out drones from Pink Floyd in Pompeii and Flaming Lips (The Embryonic LP).

200 copies on transparent vinyl from Fuzz Club / 300 transparent red trough Klangkollektivet.

Available from April 6th

name: The Woken Trees - NNON
description: The dark, gloomy debut release from the acclaimed Copenhagen rock band The Woken Trees. For a year, the six members have lived, slept and played music together in an abandoned villa outside Copenhagen, and the outcome is their debut album 'NNON'. It is a desperate response to isolation, darkness and gloom and what it entails: it arises crazy thoughts and screaming your insides out!

name: Singapore Sling - Never Forever
description:
Singapore Sling is a darkly psychedelic band from Reykjavik, Iceland. They are inexplicable and elusive but remind one of the drugged out soul power bands like Jesus and Mary Chain and My Bloody Valentine. Their debut album, "The Curse Of Singapore Sling", came out in Summer 2003. To date they have 6 criticaly acclaimed studio albums under their belt and has gained fans from all over the globe. Their leader is singer-songwriter-guitarist Henrik Bjornsson, is also known from the band Dead Skeletons.

Singapore Sling - Never Forever. 12" transparent orange vinyl, 300 numbered copies, gatefold cover.

name: Sonic Jesus - Sonic Jesus
description:
Sonic Jesus is a neo-psychedelic band from Doganella di Ninfa,Italy. It's Velvet Underground, raped by Spacemen 3, dressed in neo-psychedelia, folk imprinted and shoegaze nuances. Their powerful wall of sound created by hypnotic melody and wild saturation of dark pulsating noise will take you on an unforgetable musical journey.

Sonic Jesus - Ltd 300 numbered copies. 10" vinyl. (50 copies in transparent piss yellow (Sold Out) and 250 copies in black with white splatter).

name: The Underground Youth - Delirium
description:
"Inspired by shoegaze, post-punk and psychedelic rock through the ages The Underground Youth are a Manchester band combining psychedelic and raw garage sounds with a hauntingly beautiful twist."

The Underground Youth - Delirium. Edition of 500, hand numbered, ultra clear vinyl, 180g.

name: The Underground Youth - Low Slow Needle
description:
"Inspired by shoegaze, post-punk and psychedelic rock through the ages The Underground Youth are a Manchester band combining psychedelic and raw garage sounds with a hauntingly beautiful twist."

Low Slow Needle 10". 300 copies, hand numbered, 100 copies coke bottle clear, 200 copies white opaque. 
Including digital download.

"Inspired by shoegaze, post-punk and psychedelic rock through the ages The Underground Youth are a Manchester band combining psychedelic and raw garage sounds with a hauntingly beautiful twist."

Morning Sun 7". 500 copies, black vinyl, w/ sticker

name: Piatcions - Heaven's Sins
description: Piatcons EP "Heaven's Sins" on 12" silver 180" vinyl. Limited to 300 copies.

name: The Wands
description:
The Danish psych duo, The Wands was formed in december 2011 by childhood friends, Christian Skibdal and Mads Gras. Bursting out of a creative community in Copenhagen, they played their first show in a dark living room in a house belonging to their friends, The Woken Trees.

The sound descends from early 60's psychedelia but touches on different genres. The duo always appear live with more musicians on stage and their shows have a great element of improvisation. The atmosphere is raw, yet full of colors as heavy drones and rumbling fuzz-guitars clash with catchy, light melodies, and playful psychedelic guitar-bling all topped with a distinctive Danish accent. 

Hello I Know The Blow You Grow Is Magic - Ltd 300 numbered copies. 
10" vinyl. (100 copies in transparent orange and 200 copies in ultra clear with yellow and orange haze). 
Includes digital download.

name: Black Lizard
description:
Helsinki-based Black Lizard fuses hypnotic rock music with primitive psychedelia and reverb-drenched jangly pop reminiscent of the 1960s. The four-piece, which channels hazy energy from the very roots of rock n roll, has released an EP, which features four songs that are haunting and beautiful, slow and fast, loud and hushed but still always retain that certain excitement of electric garage rock. Some have said that the band sounds a bit like modern neo-psychedelic classics such as Brian Jonestown Massacre, Black Angels or BRMC. In the last couple of years the band has played a plethora of diverse live shows, during which they have managed to create their own, distorted signature sound.

Black Lizard 10". Edition of 300. 100 transparent red & 200 classic black.

name: Christian Bland & The Revelators
description: Christian Bland is best known as the guitarist for The Black Angels. His solo project, Christian Bland and The Revelators highlights his signature sound and contributions to one of modern psychedelic rock's biggest bands, while providing an open canvas to explore different ideas and influences. Pig Boat Blues is a collection of 16 tracks recorded 2009-2011 at Laguna Studio in Austin, Texas.

name: AUSTIN PSYCH FEST 3 DVD
description: The Austin Psych Fest 3 DVD features highlight performances from the 2010 festival. Bands in the film include The Raveonettes, The Black Angels, Silver Apples, Warpaint, Spindrift, The Warlocks, Pink Mountaintops, Headdress, Ringo Deathstarr and more. Produced and directed by Oswald James with live audio recorded and mixed by The Pirate Studio. 1 hr 24 min, 16:9 widescreen, Region 1 DVD.

name: Austin Psych Fest 2011 "LIVE AT THE POWER PLANT" DVD
description:
This feature length film documents the 2011 festival, held at the historical Seaholm Power Plant.

Directed and produced by Alta Real Pictures; audio recorded and mixed by Elevation Reservation. Austin Psych Fest : Live at the Power Plant features performances from the following artists, in order of appearance:

name: The Vacant Lost - High & Low / Let Me Out
description: High & Low" b/w "Let Me Out" is the second official single release by The Vacant Lots. Formed by Jared Artaud and Brian MacFadyen, the duo takes as much inspiration from Bo Diddley and The Stooges as it does from Andy Warhol and Arthur Rimbaud. They have developed their own sound, producing an immense, unrelenting, sonic assault with just two people, combining a minimalist aesthetic of rock n roll with hypnotic guitar riffs, Native American influenced drumming, electronic drones, poetry-driven lyrics and live visual projections.

name: The Lucid Dream - Erbistock Mill
description:
The Lucid Dream were formed in Carlisle, Cumbria, in 2008. Most recently, the band were selected as full UK tour support to A Place To Bury Strangers in May 2012, and followed this up in June 2012, supporting Death In Vegas. This was on the back of supports to Spectrum, Crocodiles, Captain Beefheart's 'The Magic Band', and The Aliens, to name a few.

Erbistock Mill 10". Edition of 300, hand numbered, transparent red vinyl. Including digital download.
